caption.body: In Katy Wang’s thesis film for London’s Kingston University, a solitary astronaut sends out a signal for others in a story that reflects the filmmaker’s feelings of loneliness and her desire for contact while experiencing a long-distance relationship.  See "Contact" by Katy Wang, now playing in the Video Arts Room located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2RuCry0 . . .
